00:02:47,347 --> 00:02:50,737
- Dobro jutro.
- Mozete li da mi rasitnite novac?

4
00:02:50,947 --> 00:02:53,939
Retko dolaze ljudi
sa 500 franaka.

5
00:02:55,147 --> 00:02:56,660
Dajte mi.

6
00:03:09,947 --> 00:03:12,541
- Ko je to?
- Zar ne znate?

7
00:03:13,947 --> 00:03:17,383
Najbolji je od svih!

8
00:03:19,707 --> 00:03:21,937
Kaniak!

9
00:03:22,147 --> 00:03:24,536
Daniel Kaniak!

10
00:03:25,547 --> 00:03:28,778
On je iz Selizije.
I moj je prijatelj!

11
00:03:32,827 --> 00:03:35,819
Na slici izgleda
kao druga osoba.

12
00:03:35,947 --> 00:03:38,859
Isli smo u istu skolu kao klinci.

13
00:03:39,067 --> 00:03:42,616
Ozbiljan sam.

14
00:03:44,147 --> 00:03:48,902
Znate li gde mogu da ga nadjem?
Da mu se javim.

15
00:03:49,107 --> 00:03:51,860
U hotelu Champs-ElysÈeses.

16
00:03:52,067 --> 00:03:55,742
- Kako da stignem tamo?
- Taksijem.

17
00:05:09,947 --> 00:05:13,303
Ja sam Kaniakov prijatelj.
Isli smo zajedno u skolu...

18
00:05:13,507 --> 00:05:16,977
...u Oslovic.
- A, Oslovic! - Da!

19
00:06:21,867 --> 00:06:24,335
Andreas!

20
00:06:24,547 --> 00:06:26,538
Daniele.

21
00:06:29,187 --> 00:06:33,180
Andreas, prijatelju moj.

22
00:06:34,147 --> 00:06:37,139
Moj najbolji drug.

23
00:07:05,147 --> 00:07:08,139
Zelim da ti poklonim odelo.

24
00:07:09,947 --> 00:07:13,940
Poslednjih nekoliko dana
su mi bili predivni.

25
00:07:14,147 --> 00:07:20,143
- Imam skoro 1000 franaka u dzepu!
- Znas sta? Ja imam oko 1000 odela u ormaru.

26
00:07:20,347 --> 00:07:22,941
Bilo bi mi zadovoljstvo da
ti poklonim jedno od njih.

27
00:07:23,147 --> 00:07:26,139
Secas se dok smo bili u skoli.

28
00:07:26,347 --> 00:07:29,339
Uvek si mi dopustao
da prepisujem od tebe.

29
00:07:31,547 --> 00:07:36,257
Pa, sta kazes?
Gde zivis, poslacu ti.

30
00:07:39,947 --> 00:07:41,938
Ne mozes da ga posaljes.

31
00:07:42,147 --> 00:07:44,786
- Zasto ne?
- Jer nemam adresu.

32
00:07:48,947 --> 00:07:53,941
- Ja spavam ispod novina.
- Naci cu ti sobu u hotelu.

33
00:08:05,547 --> 00:08:08,061
Ovuda, gospodo.

34
00:08:29,947 --> 00:08:35,658
Ako ti zatreba nesto,
samo pozvoni i zatrazi.

35
00:08:36,947 --> 00:08:44,103
Kako bih ti se zahvalio, 
vodim te na jedno posebno mesto.

36
00:09:35,827 --> 00:09:39,740
Sada ce doci devojke.
Volis li da igras?

37
00:09:39,947 --> 00:09:42,939
Da, ali za mene je vec kasno.

38
00:10:16,147 --> 00:10:18,456
- Laku noc.
- Laku noc.

39
00:10:23,547 --> 00:10:28,539
Andreas, sutra ti saljem dva odela.
Zasto? - Zasto da ne?

40
00:10:29,107 --> 00:10:32,941
Jedno je sasvim dovoljno.

41
00:10:33,147 --> 00:10:37,379
- Treba li ti novac?
- Jos uvek imam 900 franaka.

42
00:10:37,587 --> 00:10:39,418
Cao.

43
00:10:41,547 --> 00:10:43,265
Vidimo se.

44
00:13:37,187 --> 00:13:39,621
Veoma si lepa.

45
00:13:47,187 --> 00:13:48,745
I ti si takodje.

46
00:13:52,147 --> 00:13:54,707
Mogu li ponovo da te vidim?

47
00:13:58,747 --> 00:14:02,217
- Sutra, mozda.
- U redu.

48
00:16:40,547 --> 00:16:42,936
Da li zelis da me pitas nesto?

49
00:16:44,947 --> 00:16:46,938
Da.

50
00:16:48,787 --> 00:16:51,779
Ne mogu da cekam do sutra.

51
00:17:33,947 --> 00:17:39,101
- Volis knjige?
- Kad nemam sta bolje da radim.

52
00:17:44,147 --> 00:17:46,138
Ja ne citam.

53
00:17:46,347 --> 00:17:48,338
Nemam knjiga.

54
00:17:50,747 --> 00:17:53,136
Ali imam mnogo vremena.

55
00:17:54,347 --> 00:17:59,944
Ja sam ovde jos par dana,
najvise do nedelje.

56
00:18:00,147 --> 00:18:03,139
U ponedeljak moram da budem na sceni...

57
00:18:03,347 --> 00:18:05,338
...u Kanu.

58
00:18:07,547 --> 00:18:11,779
- Ti si umetnica!
- Ja sam plesacica u kazinu.

59
00:18:12,947 --> 00:18:16,622
Zar nisi do sada cuo moje ime?
Gebi.

60
00:18:17,827 --> 00:18:19,818
Gebi.

61
00:18:20,787 --> 00:18:24,063
- A, da!
- Znas moje ime?

62
00:18:25,787 --> 00:18:28,699
Naravno, iz novina.

63
00:18:38,147 --> 00:18:40,581
A sada?

64
00:20:17,667 --> 00:20:21,706
OD TVOG PRIJATELJA, DANIJEL KONIAKA

65
00:21:01,307 --> 00:21:04,982
Gde ides, tako lepo obucen?

66
00:21:06,147 --> 00:21:11,062
Imamo jos jedan dan zajedno
pre nego sto odem u Kan.

67
00:21:11,267 --> 00:21:13,303
Odvescu te u...

68
00:21:13,507 --> 00:21:15,543
...Fontainebleau.

69
00:21:16,907 --> 00:21:20,297
I jos jednu noc.

70
00:22:22,347 --> 00:22:24,338
Izvolite.

71
00:22:28,707 --> 00:22:30,902
Sta preporucujete?

72
00:22:32,547 --> 00:22:35,539
Imamo sve sto zelite...

73
00:22:43,547 --> 00:22:45,742
Jesi li bila vec ovde?

74
00:22:46,787 --> 00:22:48,778
Sta zelis?

75
00:22:52,147 --> 00:22:54,456
Vec znam sta zelis.

76
00:22:56,147 --> 00:22:58,138
Znas?

77
00:23:41,707 --> 00:23:43,937
Sta to radis?

78
00:23:44,147 --> 00:23:47,537
- Moram da platim dug.
- U nedelju?

79
00:23:47,747 --> 00:23:49,738
Da.

80
00:24:01,547 --> 00:24:04,937
Vec malo kasnim.
Zato moram da krenem.

81
00:24:05,147 --> 00:24:09,538
- Kome dugujes novac? Coveku ili zeni?
- Devojci po imenu Tereza.

82
00:24:09,747 --> 00:24:13,217
- Gubi se gade! Napolje!
- Hej!

83
00:24:17,547 --> 00:24:19,538
Cao.

84
00:26:46,947 --> 00:26:48,938
Andreas!

85
00:26:49,147 --> 00:26:51,422
- Voitek!
- Andreas!

86
00:27:01,147 --> 00:27:06,346
- Andreas! - Mozes li da me sacekas
ovde dok se ne zavrsi misa?

87
00:27:06,547 --> 00:27:11,541
Sta? Misa? Nisi se valjda
sprijateljio sa svestenicima?

88
00:27:11,747 --> 00:27:17,743
- Ne, moram da vidim malu Terezu.
- Zbog cega? - Dugujem joj novac.

89
00:27:17,947 --> 00:27:21,940
- To je dug koji moram da vratim maloj svetici.
- Koliko joj dugujes?

90
00:27:22,147 --> 00:27:24,138
200 franaka.

91
00:27:25,947 --> 00:27:28,939
Onda, idem sa tobom, je li to u redu?

92
00:27:55,547 --> 00:27:58,619
Cekaj, sta radis? 
Sta nije u redu?

93
00:28:01,947 --> 00:28:04,336
U nevolji sam.

94
00:28:04,547 --> 00:28:07,539
Momak me ceka napolju.
Moram da mu vratim 200 franaka.

95
00:28:07,747 --> 00:28:14,141
Ako mu ne vratim,
uhapsice me.

96
00:28:15,347 --> 00:28:18,339
Trebalo je da mi kazes.

97
00:28:19,547 --> 00:28:21,617
Nisam imao hrabrosti.

98
00:28:25,627 --> 00:28:27,618
Razumem te.

99
00:28:29,947 --> 00:28:32,461
Bio sam u tvojim cipelama.

100
00:28:35,787 --> 00:28:38,779
Nemoj da brines.

101
00:28:41,547 --> 00:28:43,538
Uzmi novac...

102
00:28:44,947 --> 00:28:46,938
... meni nije potreban.

103
00:28:55,947 --> 00:28:58,700
- Vidimo se u baru!
- Shh!

104
00:30:57,947 --> 00:31:00,336
Andreas!

105
00:31:00,547 --> 00:31:02,936
Dodji!

106
00:31:03,147 --> 00:31:05,138
Sedi!

107
00:31:08,747 --> 00:31:12,740
- Ti si pravi prijatelj!
- Kako da ne budemo prijatelji...

108
00:31:12,947 --> 00:31:20,058
... nakon svega sto smo prosli.
- Prijatelji po svemu i u svemu!

109
00:32:12,387 --> 00:32:14,537
Znas...

110
00:32:14,747 --> 00:32:18,137
Znao sam plesacicu
iz kazina.

111
00:32:18,347 --> 00:32:20,338
- Zaista?
- Da.

112
00:32:28,627 --> 00:32:31,619
Bio sam zaljubljen dva dana.

113
00:32:32,747 --> 00:32:36,865
Ja mogu da se zaljubim
za 10 minuta.

114
00:32:37,067 --> 00:32:39,058
Verujes li?

115
00:32:51,827 --> 00:32:55,820
- Znas li koji je dan danas?
- Nisam siguran.

116
00:32:56,027 --> 00:33:02,660
Nemam predstavu. Vidimo se u nedelju, 
isto mesto, isto vreme.

117
00:33:04,107 --> 00:33:06,098
Vidimo se.

118
00:34:26,027 --> 00:34:29,019
Da li ti treba novac?

119
00:34:35,147 --> 00:34:39,379
Znam. Jos uvek ti dugujem.

120
00:34:40,867 --> 00:34:42,858
Meni?

121
00:34:43,067 --> 00:34:47,219
Trebalo je da dam novac
maloj Terezi.

122
00:34:47,427 --> 00:34:53,423
Uveravam te, isao sam tamo svake nedelje.
Ali svakoga puta nesto se desavalo...

123
00:34:53,627 --> 00:34:59,623
Ocigledno si me pomesao sa nekim,
ali ne mogu a da ne primetim...

124
00:34:59,827 --> 00:35:03,945
...da si u nekim problemima.

125
00:35:04,147 --> 00:35:09,346
Kad smo vec kod male Tereze,
o kojoj si upravo pricao...

126
00:35:09,547 --> 00:35:14,746
...ja imam veliku obavezu
prema njoj...

127
00:35:14,947 --> 00:35:19,543
... tako da cu drage volje
obezbediti novac koliko god je potrebno.

128
00:35:19,747 --> 00:35:21,738
Koliko ti treba?

129
00:35:21,947 --> 00:35:23,938
200 franaka.

130
00:35:26,147 --> 00:35:28,138
Izvini.

131
00:35:40,947 --> 00:35:44,940
Uveravam te da sam i dalje
castan covek.

132
00:35:45,147 --> 00:35:49,140
- Nazalost, jos uvek nemam svoju adresu.
- Bas kao i ja.

133
00:35:49,347 --> 00:35:55,343
Ne, zaista. Dobro delo koje cinis
prihvatajuci ovu malu svotu novca...

134
00:35:55,547 --> 00:35:58,937
... je nesto sto ja nikad 
ne bih mogao da odplatim.

135
00:35:59,147 --> 00:36:04,141
Zato sto ja takodje
dugujem mnogo maloj Terezi.

136
00:36:06,147 --> 00:36:10,299
Zato hvala ti puno.

137
00:48:05,267 --> 00:48:08,384
Niste platili racun.

138
00:48:48,747 --> 00:48:50,544
Zao mi je.

139
00:50:48,947 --> 00:50:50,938
Gospodine...

140
00:51:04,787 --> 00:51:09,065
Ne morate da ga trazite.
Izgubili ste ga. Evo ga!

141
00:51:12,347 --> 00:51:16,340
Razumite da moze privuci
mnogo pijanaca.

142
00:51:16,547 --> 00:51:21,701
Cuvajte ga dobro i
budite malo oprezniji.

143
00:51:49,947 --> 00:51:51,938
Hej!

144
00:51:52,147 --> 00:51:54,138
Ja sam.

145
00:51:54,347 --> 00:51:56,941
Andreas Kartak.

146
00:51:57,147 --> 00:51:59,138
Rudar.

147
00:52:00,947 --> 00:52:02,938
U istom rudniku.

148
00:52:06,947 --> 00:52:09,097
U istom tunelu.

149
00:52:10,747 --> 00:52:14,945
Sedi ovde, prijatelju moj!

150
00:52:15,147 --> 00:52:17,138
Na pocasno mesto.

151
00:52:21,107 --> 00:52:25,339
Prijatelji uvek sede
na pocasno mesto.

152
00:52:25,547 --> 00:52:27,981
Ti si moj prijatelj, takodje.

153
00:52:28,187 --> 00:52:33,261
Prijatelji za sve i u svemu.

154
00:52:35,747 --> 00:52:37,738
Slusaj.

155
00:52:42,947 --> 00:52:46,178
Malocas mi se nesto desilo...

156
00:52:47,947 --> 00:52:53,943
Bio sam na trgu i desilo mi se
nesto zaista neobicno.

157
00:52:54,147 --> 00:52:56,820
Policajac me je zaustavio...

158
00:52:58,947 --> 00:53:03,179
...i ja sam pomislio da
ce mi traziti dokumenta.

159
00:53:04,547 --> 00:53:07,744
"Ja sam zaista u problemima."

160
00:53:07,947 --> 00:53:12,941
Umesto toga, on mi kaze da sam
izgubio novcanik...
the portfolio...

161
00:53:13,147 --> 00:53:17,140
...i daje mi novcanik
koji nije moj.

162
00:53:18,947 --> 00:53:20,938
To je Bozji znak.

163
00:53:23,147 --> 00:53:26,139
Morao sam da ga prihvatim.

164
00:53:43,147 --> 00:53:45,138
200 franaka.

165
00:53:49,147 --> 00:53:51,138
Sada...

166
00:53:52,147 --> 00:53:56,538
...idem da odplatim dug.
- Sacekaj.

167
00:53:56,747 --> 00:54:00,342
Jos uvek traje misa.

168
00:54:00,547 --> 00:54:04,825
Kada se zavrsi mozes da krenes.

169
00:54:37,547 --> 00:54:39,538
Sta radis ovde?

170
00:54:43,067 --> 00:54:46,059
Cekam moje roditelje.

171
00:54:46,267 --> 00:54:52,342
Kada se zavrsi misa,
doci ce po mene.

172
00:54:52,547 --> 00:54:55,539
Mi uvek ovako radimo
svake nedelje.

173
00:54:58,747 --> 00:55:02,342
- Hoces mi reci kako se zoves?
- Tereza.

174
00:55:11,747 --> 00:55:13,738
Tereza!

175
00:55:20,107 --> 00:55:22,098
Savrseno.

176
00:55:23,547 --> 00:55:27,938
Ja nisam nikad mislio
da svetica...

177
00:55:28,147 --> 00:55:31,537
...tako velika,
a ipak tako mala...

178
00:55:31,747 --> 00:55:35,137
... mali davalac,
a tako velik...

179
00:55:35,347 --> 00:55:43,539
... ce mi uciniti cast da dodje meni
nakon mog neuspeha toliko puta...

180
00:55:43,747 --> 00:55:48,377
... da dodjem do nje.

181
00:55:50,547 --> 00:55:52,538
Znam.

182
00:55:52,747 --> 00:55:56,899
To je tvoja delikatnost i dragocenost.

183
00:55:59,547 --> 00:56:01,981
Ja sam te izneverio.

184
00:56:03,947 --> 00:56:06,939
Dugujem ti 200 franaka...

185
00:56:07,147 --> 00:56:10,457
... koje nisam mogao da 
ti vratim toliko dugo.

186
00:56:15,107 --> 00:56:17,382
Svetice!

187
00:56:20,747 --> 00:56:23,739
Ali, vi mi nista ne dugujete.

188
00:56:29,747 --> 00:56:32,181
Ja...

189
00:56:33,947 --> 00:56:37,303
Pokusao sam toliko puta...

190
00:56:40,947 --> 00:56:43,256
- Ako vam treba...

191
00:56:44,947 --> 00:56:47,939
imam nesto novca
u torbi...

192
00:56:49,347 --> 00:56:51,338
... uzmite.

193
00:57:06,547 --> 00:57:11,746
Sada, moram da krenem,
jer misa je skoro gotova...

194
00:57:11,947 --> 00:57:15,337
...i moji roditelji ce doci.

195
00:57:31,947 --> 00:57:33,938
Voitek!

196
00:57:34,147 --> 00:57:37,537
- Pomozi.
- Andreas!

197
00:57:48,107 --> 00:57:53,101
Odnesite ga u crkvu.
Svestenik ce znati sta da radi.

198
00:58:22,307 --> 00:58:24,298
Stavite ga ovde.

199
00:58:32,147 --> 00:58:36,345
Odmaknite se, dozvolite mu da dise.

